      • pair

        public MultiCollection pair(SeriesCollection x,
                            java.lang.String xName,
                            SeriesCollection y,
                            java.lang.String yName,
                            java.lang.String groupingCriteria)
        Split each collection by groupingFields. Retain only single-series groups. Create multi-collection by pairing series from x and y by grouping key. Drop unpaired keys.
        Parameters:
        x - First collection.
        xName - By this name series of the first collection are available in multi-collection context.
        y - Second collection.
        yName - By this name series of the second collection are available in multi-collection context.
        groupingCriteria - Use this components of the SeriesKey to match series from the first collection to series from the second collection.

      • vwap

        public SeriesCollection vwap(SeriesCollection price,
                             SeriesCollection quantity)
                      throws java.io.IOException
        Calculate volume-weighed average price: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Volume-weighted_average_price per entity. For each entity:
        - find dot product of price and quantity for each tags
        - amount = sum dot products for the entity
        - totalQuantity = sum of quantities for the entity
        - vwap = amount / totalQuantity.
        Throws:
        java.io.IOException

      • vwap

                             java.lang.String interval)
                      throws java.io.IOException
        Calculate volume-weighed average price: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Volume-weighted_average_price per entity and for each interval. View vwap(SeriesCollection, SeriesCollection).
        Throws:
        java.io.IOException
